title: Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu Limited
description: Deloitte's brand colors, including vibrant green (0DF200), teal blue (3EFAC5), and aqua blue (33F0FF), reflect the company's commitment to innovation and forward-thinking. These colors, showcased in their branding materials such as in the publication from https://www2.deloitte.com/content/dam/Deloitte/pt/Documents/Temporary/Apresenta%C3%A7%C3%A3o_brand_RA2021.pdf, embody the dynamic and diverse nature of their global professional services.
